CloudFormation Stacks
=====================

This folder defines CloudFormation stacks for the application. It contains a
src folder which has python scripts that generates CloudFormation JSON files in
templates folder. These JSON templates can then be copy+pasted into the Cosmos
Admin panel for a stack for a given project.


Generating Templates
--------------------

On your CentOS 6 sandbox, install the common python libraries:

```
sudo yum install bbc-aws-cloudformation-common
```

You can then run `make` to generate new templates.


More
----

See https://confluence.dev.bbc.co.uk/display/platform/Cloud+Platform+-+Getting+Started+Guide for more information.
